Readme for /vendor
Clara Todd 
28 Aug 2017

This is the directory for libraries and functions that you may have sourced elsewhere.
Kept separately so that source control won't conflict with own project files.

Example third party vendor projects

* securimage: https://www.phpcaptcha.org/.  php library for 
  captcha bot protection for public forms. enable in config with 
  RECAPTCHA_VALIDATION constant.

* FUTURE: future form creator () todo - find replacement for pear quickform!

* FUTURE: session handle 

* FUTURE: messaging/alerts

* FUTURE: mailers
